---
import Base from '@/layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Topics">
  <section class="topics-page">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="topics-header animate-fade-up">
        <h1>Topics</h1>
        <p>Everything we've compiled so far. Each page is sourced, reviewed, and updated when things change.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="topic-list stagger">

        <a href="/topics/nhs-waiting-times" class="card topic-row">
          <div class="topic-row-content">
            <div class="topic-row-tags">
              <span class="pill pill-blue">UK</span>
              <span class="pill pill-blue">NHS</span>
            </div>
            <h3>NHS waiting times by clinic</h3>
            <p>Current waiting times at every NHS gender identity clinic in England and Scotland.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="confidence confidence-strong">
            <span class="confidence-dot"></span>
            Strong
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/topics/name-change-england-wales" class="card topic-row">
          <div class="topic-row-content">
            <div class="topic-row-tags">
              <span class="pill pill-blue">UK</span>
              <span class="pill pill-pink">Legal</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Changing your name (England & Wales)</h3>
            <p>Deed poll vs statutory declaration, where to send it, what to update.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="confidence confidence-strong">
            <span class="confidence-dot"></span>
            Strong
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/topics/blood-work-basics" class="card topic-row">
          <div class="topic-row-content">
            <div class="topic-row-tags">
              <span class="pill pill-pink">Health</span>
            </div>
            <h3>Blood work basics</h3>
            <p>What to test, target ranges, when to test, and how to read your results.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="confidence confidence-strong">
            <span class="confidence-dot"></span>
            Strong
          </span>
        </a>

      </div>

      <div class="coming-soon animate-fade-up">
        <div class="callout callout-pink">
          <p><strong>More topics coming.</strong> We're working on: UK private providers compared, what to expect from estrogen, what to expect from testosterone, voice training, hair removal, GRC application process, and where to find support (UK). <a href="mailto:charlie@harperautomation.co.uk">Suggest a topic</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .topics-page {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0 var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .topics-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .topics-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .topics-header p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .topic-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .topic-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .topic-row h3 {
    margin: var(--space-xs) 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    transition: color var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .topic-row:hover h3 {
    color: #1a7ba3;
  }

  .topic-row p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .topic-row-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .coming-soon {
    margin-top: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .topic-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
